history.content:
The question is not your grade in 54 but how well you have internalized the linear algebra material. For that, you'll need to ask yourself I guess. For most students, it takes 2-3 passes of linear algebra to gain the required mastery for an advanced course like CS 189.

--------------------------------------------

Honestly, you should be fine. You may need to review a few things if you are shaky on some concepts, but you should be able to understand what is going on.
